{"tid":175193,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖］LIHK有冇人收藏勳章？（都係玩具黎嘅）","createTime":"2017-03-27T10:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T08:55:28.000Z","uid":72679,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0efbbffdb2c32057ea7ecbb13a6134e7b5355e76","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我好鍾意去旅行個陣買一d當地嘅襟章做收藏品 漸漸就開始收藏有關軍事嘅襟章 甚至軍徽同勳章 好想知道連登有冇人係同好 仲想交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個post開係玩具台因爲唔知開咩台好<br />\n對我黎講佢地都算玩具嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PM8JJ9Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPM8JJ9Q.jpg&h=3c509db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面三個係<br />\n蘇聯第三級別勞動光榮勛章<br />\n烏克蘭勛章：defender of the motherland<br />\n蘇聯時代捷克秘密警察SNB service award<br />\n<br />\n上面兩個<br />\n列寧紀念章<br />\n捷克社會主義同志襟章"},{"pid":"4640c927f6183308cb616a28a5f3c280543af53c","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:35:21.000Z","msg":"Pish 推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15a3d7bc8cbf8564c658743d4ae4e89eef6058f","tid":175193,"uid":40297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"好正"},{"pid":"832e22a8f5d401d726e74ea6f144cf0a7007f2f8","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHi巴打 <br />\n難得有人入黎 <br />\n繼續upload下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc88ebb686fd5adb59e7b3295ce2e428183cd1ac","tid":175193,"uid":19363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"有無英美"},{"pid":"364bcb43a47a078700d389c8cadec987f288cccc","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8nay1o3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nay1o3.jpg&h=00158748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住呢幅圖會雜亂少少 因為我冇將佢地分類得好好<br />\n不過入面有好多正野<br />\n<br />\n香港義勇軍軍旗 軍徽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偽滿州國陸軍cap badge<br />\n美國陸軍軍階 有sergeant, specialist, private first class, major<br />\nDuke of Lancaster's Regiment 軍徽<br />\n俄羅斯軍徽<br />\n國民黨空軍軍徽"},{"pid":"7a54043e308168381d940f8004622c13f3d8ca27","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無英美</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eab0aa4481335379f8d7b5e66ede63dd791e9fe","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"英軍officer grade軍階<br />\n由右至左<br />\n少尉 中尉 上尉 少校 中校 上校<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/185245_bcbe676d3e7c5f1100c84d2d319ded4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F185245_bcbe676d3e7c5f1100c84d2d319ded4d.jpg&h=999c8ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個搵得勁辛苦 行咗成個倫敦先買齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外我仲有一個准尉 warrant officer嘅 不過冇影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223504c8706afe0cc0d91d51aed487d098086c93","tid":175193,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:55:32.000Z","msg":"Stolen valor"},