s/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52427ea5b7007e5d10177aae3961f045e88fc84","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:26:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013d021e0d550b2233b14921b55067c83793d387","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:33:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8d50b6fb08511c081494ecc6bb1e27717aa4294","tid":175193,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3755a13a14bfce978ebafd1b090e1e1207baccba","tid":175193,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"想睇日本  全部"},{"pid":"5465d01b3692ca021a0792fa9bd3b6f6f3162487","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇納粹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n納粹勳章係勳章市場黎講貴到仆街<br />\n坐底幾千蚊 我見過最平嘅German Mother Cross都近一千銀  我最有性趣係iron cross<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n送個大英帝國War Medal 1939-1945你睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8769d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8769d6.jpg&h=75608006&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab6f6a77067486d74869052e1bfea3f27ba7b3ae","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇日本  全部</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本除咗個偽滿州國陸軍軍徽就冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身去東京或者沖繩睇過嘅 都係賣美軍野多<br />\n另外我比較多歐洲嘅收藏"},{"pid":"d4402f9cb9b1b2b5751fd89c7333ed6e6e2b90cb","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想睇日本  全部</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本除咗個偽滿州國陸軍軍徽就冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身去東京或者沖繩睇過嘅 都係賣美軍野多<br />\n另外我比較多歐洲嘅收藏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黎緊去日本 就去睇下有冇二戰日軍野買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808c086e45f7cd9eb2e978ca94cd4f57e894b59f","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:10:10.000Z","msg":"Pish 有冇人都有收藏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b68b47cac477115dc6a648c3d92dd2797728269","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:44:36.000Z","msg":"Pish 呢度有冇人收藏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc436f1886840654746df87538605a9021c9e1f2","tid":175193,"uid":72679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:35:27.000Z","msg":"雖然好似冇人睇 <br />\n不過都up多個收藏品<br />\n就係比War Medal高一個級別嘅Defense Medal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p98doDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp98doDA.jpg&h=8bb08a9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e7767f85d492a3edb96fbe270eb6bb1403c5f0c","tid":175193,"uid":40297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces